highlights.text: “伯虎说 - DJ阳少版” by 伯爵Johnny and 唐伯虎Annie is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #74.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 224 days straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #7.
“Twenty-Five” by Song Ji Eun is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 35 spots at #35.
